<div id="review_1499907593" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1499907593" />
    <a title="Bfisher" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/6432978-bfisher"><img alt="Bfisher" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1499907593?book_show_action=true">Jan 07, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Bfisher" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Bfisher" href="/user/show/6432978-bfisher">Bfisher</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/6432978-bfisher?shelf=literature">literature</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1499907593" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6002268161429059972">If Goodreads had a ten-star rating scheme, I would have wanted to give this book eleven stars. This book is a message from the dark heart of the darkest century. Everyone should read this book; if they did, it might help make the 21st century less calamitous than the 20th century.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

