              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/545336-mike?shelf=ww2">ww2</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer149508270" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12282864690787086679"><i>Scheissbegleiter</i>...really, how can anyone understand such a thing? Primo Levi takes you into the awful hell of Auschwitz to show you what life was like and how they survived or not. Such a powerful book and one that everyone should read at some time. After a &quot;selection&quot; of prisoners who will soon depart for the gas chambers, Levi sees one praying and thanking G0d that he was not selected. How can one imagine a &quot;Providence&quot; in such a time? <b>5 Stars</b> It was truly amazing.</span>
  <span id="freeText12282864690787086679" style="display:none"><i>Scheissbegleiter</i>...really, how can anyone understand such a thing? Primo Levi takes you into the awful hell of Auschwitz to show you what life was like and how they survived or not. Such a powerful book and one that everyone should read at some time. After a "selection" of prisoners who will soon depart for the gas chambers, Levi sees one praying and thanking G0d that he was not selected. How can one imagine a "Providence" in such a time? <b>5 Stars</b> It was truly amazing.</span>
